<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pago Fallido - Metal-Ce</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .failure-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 100px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .failure-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .failure-title {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="failure-container">
        <i class="fas fa-times-circle failure-icon"></i>
        <h1 class="failure-title">Pago No Completado</h1>
        <p class="lead">Hubo un problema al procesar tu pago</p>
        
        <p>No se realizó ningún cargo. Puedes intentar nuevamente.</p>

        <div class="mt-4">
            <a href="/checkout" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Reintentar
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Volver al Inicio
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
